<HEADLINE>
FT  19 AUG 94 / Car output rises 3.8% in quarter
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Car production rose a seasonally adjusted 3.8 per cent in the three months
to July compared with the previous three months. Production for export rose
6.5 per cent and home production rose 1.9 per cent, the Central Statistical
Office said.
Compared with the same three months a year ago total car production also
rose a seasonally adjusted 3.8 per cent.
